title: Book are Magical
author: sameeksha
text: books are a magical wonderland,   explaining many things hard to understand  books can take you to many places,   they can be about anything in most cases.   they take you to locations near and far,   they can even take you to a star,   oh,  what a wonderful thing they are!  books can educate the rich and the poor,   about math,  english or any answer you look for,   they can teach you what is right or wrong,   or tell you why a giraffeâ’s neck is so long.   they can help you study for a test,   or tell you how to get rid of a pest.   books can give you lots of knowledge,   and help you go to school and college.   they can help you become a mayor,   or make you feel like you are in the air,   in fact they can take you anywhere! â  books tell many different stories,   of people,  their past,  and their glories.   books at the library are for free,   telling stories,  facts,  and countries to see.   they can tell you where to find a hot air balloon,   or about a movie coming up soon.   indeed they are mankindâ’s biggest boon!  made up stories are called fiction,   sometimes they are so good they can cause addiction.   the stories with good imagination can get you lost,   and you read,  and enjoy,  and forget all costs  oh,  how many things we can learn from it,   new words,  new languages,  and how to stay fit  they can tell yummy recipes great for cooks,   these are some of the wonderful things about books!
